//TEXT
<jaT0001>If she comes in now, I'll be able to surprise her. I began preparing my attack and set up for the perfect ambush.
<enT0001>If she comes in now, I'll be able to surprise her. I began preparing my attack and set up for the perfect ambush.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>Then the silence of the laboratory was shattered by piercing noise.
<enT0002>Then the silence of the laboratory was shattered by piercing noise.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0003>"Wha..."
<enT0003>"Wha..."

//TEXT
<jaT0004>Surprised, I searched for the sound. It was coming from the transceiver I used before. Someone was trying to contact me.
<enT0004>Surprised, I searched for the sound. It was coming from the transceiver I used before. Someone was trying to contact me.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0005>"(Shit! I left it on the last time I used it...)"
<enT0005>"(Shit! I left it on the last time I used it...)"

//TEXT
<jaT0006>I could sense the blood drain from my cheeks. I couldn't possibly surprise her with this damn thing.
<enT0006>I could sense the blood drain from my cheeks. I couldn't possibly surprise her with this damn thing.

//TEXT
<jaT0007>I quickly drew my gun and tried to get away from the door, but I was already too late.
<enT0007>I quickly drew my gun and tried to get away from the door, but I was already too late.

//TEXT
<jaT0008>The automatic door opened, and Yu came in. With no mercy, she fired a barrage straight at me.
<enT0008>The automatic door opened, and Yu came in. With no mercy, she fired a barrage straight at me.

//TEXT
<jaT0009>Helpless against the countless bullets, my body sprung back like a toy with a coiled spring.
<enT0009>Helpless against the countless bullets, my body sprung back like a toy with a coiled spring.

//TEXT
<jaT0010>......
<enT0010>......

//TEXT
